Class XmlFileSystemResource

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.paypal.selion.platform.dataprovider.FileSystemResource
      • com.paypal.selion.platform.dataprovider.XmlFileSystemResource

  • public class XmlFileSystemResource
extends FileSystemResource
    Extends FileSystemResource class to support XML file as a DataProvider to be used by XmlDataProvider.
